---
import LayoutMinimal from "../layouts/LayoutMinimal.astro";
import IntroModal from "../components/IntroModal.astro";
---

<LayoutMinimal title="Ryan Eberhard" description="Fractional product & growth leadership for venture-backed startups" ogImage="/og/home.png">
  <header class="header">
    <div class="header__inner">
      <a href="/" class="header__logo"><img src="/gauges-green-g-core.svg" alt="" class="header__mark" />Ryan Eberhard</a>
    </div>
    <nav class="header__nav">
      <a href="/" class="active">home</a>
      <span class="header__nav-sep">·</span>
      <a href="/experience">experience</a>
      <span class="header__nav-sep">·</span>
      <a href="/services">services</a>
      <span class="header__nav-sep">·</span>
      <a href="/log">writing</a>
      <span class="header__nav-sep">·</span>
      <a href="mailto:eberhard@gaugesgreen.com">contact</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <div class="home-intro">
    <img src="/perfil.jpg" alt="Ryan Eberhard" class="headshot" />
    <p>
      Your portfolio company is 2-3 quarters post-investment and the metrics aren't moving. I help you figure out why. Then we fix it together.
    </p>
    <p>
      I was CPO at <a href="https://ziprecruiter.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">ZipRecruiter</a> for seven years. We took it from Series A to NYSE, $100M to $900M in revenue. Since then I've run turnarounds at <a href="https://jobget.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">JobGet</a> and <a href="https://swingeducation.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Swing Education</a>, stepping in when the numbers stopped making sense.
    </p>
    <p>
      I start with a 2-4 week diagnostic: what's broken, what's fixable, and a 30/60/90 plan. If there's a fit, I embed for a transformational quarter and ship what actually moves the needle.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you have a company that's doing the work but stuck, <a href="/schedule">let's talk</a>.
    </p>
  </div>

  <footer class="footer">
    <a href="mailto:eberhard@gaugesgreen.com">email</a>
    <span class="header__nav-sep">·</span>
    <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/eberhard" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">linkedin</a>
    <span class="header__nav-sep">·</span>
    <a href="/schedule">book a call</a>
    <span class="header__nav-sep">·</span>
    <button class="intro-trigger footer-btn">make intro</button>
  </footer>

  <IntroModal />
</LayoutMinimal>

<style>
  .footer-btn {
    background: none;
    border: none;
    font-family: inherit;
    font-size: inherit;
    color: var(--dim);
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .footer-btn:hover {
    color: var(--text);
  }
</style>
